---
title: Shawarma-Style Turkey Wraps with Garlic Sauce and Spinach Salad
description: We're serving up a truly delicious twist on a Canadian favourite that will definitely excite your tastebuds! Spiced turkey wrapped up with fresh tomatoes and parsley and topped with a sweet garlic sauce may just remind you of the famous East Coast-style donairs.
